TASK 3

for loop possibilities
1)
class ForEg{
public static void main(String[] args){ 
   int i=90;
  for(;i>100;i++){
  System.out.println("hi");
}
}
}
Result: compiled and get no error but result is blank

2)
class ForEg{
public static void main(String[] args){ 
   int i=90;
  for(;i>100;i--){
  System.out.println("hi");
}
}
}
Result: compiled and get no error but result is blank

3)
class ForEg{
public static void main(String[] args){ 
   int i=90;
for(; ;i++){
  System.out.println("hi");
}
}
}
Result: compiled and output is hi up to so on

4)
class ForEg{
public static void main(String[] args){ 
   int i=90;
for(;i<100;i++){
  System.out.println("hi");
}
}
}
Result: 
hi
hi
hi
hi
hi
hi
hi
hi
hi
hi

4)
class ForEg{
public static void main(String[] args){ 
   
int i=90;
for(;i<100;i+=2){
  System.out.println("hi");
}
}
}
Result:
hi
hi
hi
hi
hi
